{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Jarack Volff |image = Jarack Volff.jpeg |caption = Jarack Volff |category = Normal Minor Enemy<br/ >[[Challenge Battle Enemy (XC3)|Challenge Battle Enemy]] |type = [[Volff]] |level = 53-54<br/ >70 |area = [[Captocorn Peak]] |spawntime = Anytime<br/ >During ''[[Men! Of! The Sea! IV]]'' |respawn = Yes<br/ >No |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = }} '''Jarack Volffs''' are Normal Enemies in {{XC3}}. They are members of the [[Volff]] family, and can be found at level 53-54 on [[Captocorn Peak]] in the [[Aetia Region]]. They may drop legendary [[Volffskin]], which is needed for the [[gem]] [[Refined Blessing|Refined Blessing X]]. One is fought at level 70 during the third wave of the [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] ''[[Men! Of! The Sea! IV]]''. {{clr}}
